### Comparison Table — Quick Revision

| Feature | Teacher-Centred | Learner-Centred |
|---|---|---|
| Role of teacher | Instructor, authority | Facilitator, guide |
| Role of student | Passive listener | Active participant |
| Focus | Syllabus coverage | Skill development |
| Examples | Lecture, demonstration | Seminar, PBL, role-play |
| Suitable for | Large classes, foundational knowledge | Critical thinking, application |

| Feature | SWAYAM | SWAYAM PRABHA |
|---|---|---|
| Medium | Internet (website/app) | DTH satellite TV |
| Access requirement | Smartphone/computer + internet | TV + DTH set-top box |
| Interactivity | High (quizzes, forums) | Low (one-way broadcast) |
| Credit transfer | Yes (with proctored exams) | No direct credit |
| Target audience | All with internet access | Rural/remote learners |

