### Exam-Likely Questions and Answers

**Q: Which of the following is a learner-centred method?**
→ Seminar ✓ (not lecture, not demonstration)

**Q: SWAYAM was launched in which year?**
→ 2017

**Q: Swayam Prabha uses which medium to broadcast?**
→ DTH (Direct to Home) satellite television

**Q: Which MOOC type focuses on connectivity and network-based learning?**
→ cMOOC (Connectivist MOOC)

**Q: The flipped classroom is best described as:**
→ A blended approach where content is delivered online at home and classroom time is used for active learning.

**Q: In Problem-Based Learning, the starting point is:**
→ A problem (not content/syllabus)

**Q: The "Heuristic method" was proposed by:**
→ H.E. Armstrong

